336
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:41,791
The exorcism was on Friday.

337
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:44,155
Well, today is Monday.

338
00:31:45,800 --> 00:31:48,917
And yet, I think there may be credence
to what you say.

339
