As a matter of fact,
I know there is.

340
00:31:54,600 --> 00:31:56,477
Sin Eater.

341
00:31:56,640 --> 00:32:00,838
A renegade providing a path to heaven
outside of the Church and our Savior.

342
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:05,278
