has the will to dispatch.

352
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:50,391
Thank God we still have the tools.

353
00:32:55,080 --> 00:32:59,153
The instrument of delivery, if you will.

354
00:32:59,440 --> 00:33:01,590
Now, if you'll excuse me...

355
00:33:01,760 --> 00:33:05,150
...there are more pressing matters
weighing on the Vatican tonight.

356
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:09,790
Signorina.

357
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:16,588
MARA: What could be
more important than this?

358
00:33:17,840 --> 00:33:21,230
