381
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:06,514
Go upstairs and get some sleep.

382
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,279
-Night.
ALEX: Night.

383
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:13,000
THOMAS: Sweet dreams, yeah.
MARA: You too.

384
00:35:15,120 --> 00:35:20,274
