389
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:37,473
She sees things differently.

390
00:35:38,080 --> 00:35:41,629
She feels things differently.

391
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:47,358
I wish, I wish I never saw her face.

392
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:50,115
AIex, you're a fool.

393
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:54,149
Same as you were, once.

394
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:59,669
THOMAS: Your head rules your heart.
