473
00:43:22,200 --> 00:43:26,671
As for me,
I was hoisted up by me own petard.

474
00:43:30,240 --> 00:43:31,593
Mara...

475
00:43:31,760 --> 00:43:33,671
...if I can ask...

476
00:43:34,040 --> 00:43:36,600
