between you and AIex?

477
00:43:37,560 --> 00:43:39,516
MARA:
It's okay.

478
00:43:40,000 --> 00:43:42,070
If I was embarrassed,
I'd wear bracelets.

479
00:43:45,600 --> 00:43:50,151
My Iittle brother was murdered
